won't need as many regulations

00:30:06.630 --> 00:30:08.730
about the safety of products.

00:30:08.730 --> 00:30:10.650
We hopefully won't
need as many ecolabels

00:30:10.650 --> 00:30:14.240
to guide people towards safer,
greener, healthier products.

